convert_outfiles module

Converts agrprod.out files.

convert_outfiles.convert_crop_outfiles(crop_type)

Reads agr. dem. .OUT files and saves the data in numpy .npy format.

Parameters:

crop_type (str) – determines whether the demand files being read contain food crop, fodder or bioenergy crop data.

convert_outfiles.convert_management_outfiles(manage_type)

Reads management data .OUT files; saves the data in numpy .npy format.

Parameters:

manage_type (str) – determines whether the demand files being read contain management factors, grazing intensities or harvest fractions.
